Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛·阿瑪米克·長穀部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.81,0:00:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長穀部
