Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十五年後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}\N \N最 \N \N重 \N \N要 \N \N的 \N \N人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說夠了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說一些根本無法讓人明白的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓孩子們害怕 有什麼好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在陳述事實而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙是我的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個孩子行蹤不明 應該由我來找
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是由於隧道效果而消失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說找就可以找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隧道什麼什麼的 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是重複了好幾遍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙發生了量子現象的可能性...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了完全不明白你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我回去吧 老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才26歲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那你化這麼醜的妝的理由是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水桶體型難道就是你自滿的原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪惠她..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來遙不是說過她被誰盯上了的話麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙盯上的原來是遙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯上 你說誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 我不要求你馬上就能相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果發生了什麼事 請照上面的方式聯絡我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生 請讓我在這附近再調查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 好像很了不起似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內閣 調查室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 必須去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅秧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來處置鴉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續這樣把他放任不管的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是龍騎兵的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻不容緩 把鴉給...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是為鴉著想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 大概在和以前的老朋友見面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好奇怪的人呢 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗麗 以後可不能再跑到地上去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 梟 對媽媽可要保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 我可不想讓她多操心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 梟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟從以前就認識媽媽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就像你這麼小的時候就認識了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有聽說過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽小時侯的朋友裏也有一個叫遙的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也交了一個同樣名字的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的這裏就是我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼地上什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你們的時代開始五年後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界發生了大變革
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以我們的城市為契機開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在還不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有量子世界才存在的德克菲列斯狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生在一般世界裏的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德克菲列斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太難的事情我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑呢 美保呢 勇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在這個世界裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使活著 也與你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你的世界沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 這不是我們的未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只不過是無數的未來的其中一個罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說 這只不過是一個可能性的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我們來說 你也只是過去的可能性之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是未來 卻又不是未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你雖然存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對於我們來說 可能是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣實在太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也就在這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你或許還無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是宇宙的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來也好 過去也好 甚至是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是混沌之中的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我和你 都在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 如果你能得救的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能明白你想從燕雀手裏保護龍之轉矩的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:08:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀打算把龍之轉矩從時空中消除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是引起數碼狀態崩潰的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個遙 是和我們存在的時空所不同的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論那和你過去的世界有多麼相似
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是因為我們轉移到了那裏才存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人 一定是秘密情報部的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫馬傑斯帝克特雷布的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是調查宇宙人的組織 你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:08:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 終於宇宙人要來入侵地球了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢 藤原君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙人可是挖走了牛的內臟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了 遙一定是被宇宙人抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴 美保 不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 我也是真的在擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪惠 該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機好像不通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 都是通話留言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙總是會忘記帶手機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經七點了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我擔心啊 擔心啊 擔心啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(才沒有呢)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界的我 怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩一定不能交給拉庫利瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嚮往於香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想逃離命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的命運是被詛咒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去 未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想要得到拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來香格里拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇 竟然來龍的巢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗麗好像很健康啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還是一樣任性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像她媽媽 和她簡直一個模子裏刻出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變的不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子和我們認識的遙實在太像了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是正常的 因為是近似的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還要再一次拋棄遙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去想了 阿瑪米克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越想越會陷入混沌之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻色子發生確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}玻色子：具有整數自旋的亞原子粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替換模式 香格里拉侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久以後龍之轉矩就會指出正確道路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全的防禦措施
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不出錯誤就沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉 潘朵拉 宇宙的眾神請快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉 潘朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向井 還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要讓他們放回遙 給我認真的祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不一定是宇宙人...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉 潘朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的眾神請快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪惠 是認真的嗎 不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男孩子沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不怎麼舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要叫人過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把遙還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了 一直以來很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命反映 粒子反應 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子和電腦連接沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請指示 阿瑪米克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去 放我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座標固定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍騎兵出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設置安定 進入第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我升上來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是再也見不到大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 好想再見你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩 出現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熵上升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,層流反應開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來啦 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使拉庫利瑪毀滅了也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護遙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不想失去遙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要保護那個孩子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的存在本身也許就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我還存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要保護遙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時空安定 命令返回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能讓我們的世界結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.57,0:23:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.07,0:24:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.94,0:24:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏天的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.42,0:24:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.44,0:24:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉是十五年後的佑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.10,0:25:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們親手來處置
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.98,0:25:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 秘密的事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.67,0:25:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我保守秘密嗎


